                          ===========================
                          Advance Binary Installation
                          ===========================

As root or user type:

    ./configure

and as root type:

    make install

The binaries are installed in /usr/local/bin, the documentation
in /usr/local/share/doc/advance, the program data files in
/usr/local/share/advance and the host configuration files in /usr/local/etc.

Please note that the /usr/local/ path is harcoded in the binary, you cannot
change it with the configure script.

